videos.description: Jared Harper hits a wide-open 3-pointer from the top of the arch and hits his second one from the wing.
videos.headline: Tigers' Harper knocks down back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Jared Harper makes a deep three-pointer from  the edge of the center court logo.
videos.headline: Auburn's Harper banks one in from downtown

videos.description: Mustapha Heron drains a three-pointer right at the shot clock.
videos.headline: Tigers' Heron hits 3 at shot clock

videos.description: Jared Harper intercepts the pass and chucks it to Mustapha Heron who drives for the layup.
videos.headline: Auburn steal leads to lay-in

videos.description: Bryce Brown shows off his handle and drains a three-pointer with a step-back jumper.
videos.headline: Tigers' Brown shakes and bakes for 3

videos.description: Auburn's Chuma Okeke drives into the paint and gets the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Okeke slams one home for the Tigers

videos.description: Chuma Okeke drains a three-pointer from the wing at the first half buzzer.
videos.headline: Auburn's Okeke hits 1st half buzzer beater

videos.description: Bryce Brown shows off his handle before draining a triple from the top of the arc.
videos.headline: Tigers' Brown sinks three-pointer

videos.description: Bryce Brown is on fire and has been draining shots from across the court.
videos.headline: Brown has scored  Auburn's last 13 points

videos.description: Malik Dunbar drills a corner three. Auburn finishes the game with a new season-high 17 made 3-pointers in a game.
videos.headline: Auburn sets new season-high for 3-pointers
